'''Chief Councilor''' was the title of the head of a [[Council]]. The [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] was styled Chief Councilor of the [[New Republic Provisional Council|Provisional Council]]. Chief Councilor was also an informal title of the [[First Secretary]] of the [[Combined Bothan Clans|Bothan Council]].

